{{version017}}
'''Summon Beast''' is a monster-only spell which summons a hostile [[hell beast]] into existence. Although they aren't very dangerous individually, swarms of them can trample you around the battlefield and deal surprisingly high amounts of damage. These beasts are not worth any [[experience]].

You can duplicate the effect of Summon Beast by blowing the [[horn of Geryon]], doing so can summon hell beasts which can be allied or hostile depending on your [[Evocations]] skill.

